2. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper uses deep learning to predict natural language labels for image-based components in mobile apps. 
3. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possible category as the paper deals with natural language processing and generation. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning to solve a real-world problem. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper uses deep learning to develop a model for predicting natural language labels.
